INSERT INTO votes VALUES(10374,'Ity fampiharana ity dia ahafahan''ny mpampiasa mamaritra vondron''ny session fifadiana ary manome famantaranandro miaraka amin''ny fanehoana hita maso sy re rehefa tapaky ny fifadiana iray na vita manontolo.',1779702045428,65,10,5);
INSERT INTO votes VALUES(10375,'Azafady, nisy hadisoana nitranga teo am-pitahirizana.',1779702045431,65,10,6);
INSERT INTO votes VALUES(10378,'Voaforona soa aman-tsara ny rakitra fiarovana!',1779702045438,65,10,9);
